title: Bugged Match History
body:
Yo!

Im having troubles with the match history today. I can't load any of my matches from 7PM (Australia time) from the client and op.gg. Anyone else experiencing the same thing?

replies.body:
Hi

It seems to be affecting a lot of people, not just you.  We're trying to track down the cause now :)

Cheers!
